@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Login to get JWT token
POST {{host}}/api/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "admin@admin.com",
  "password": "A2m!nPassword",
  "rememberMe": false,
  "deviceDetails": "REST Client"
}

### Get Live TV Categories (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/live/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Live TV Streams (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/live/streams?categoryId=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get VOD Categories (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/vod/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get VOD Streams (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/vod/streams?categoryId=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get VOD Info (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/vod/52356
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Series Categories (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/series/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Series (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/series?categoryId=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Series Info (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/series/12345
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get EPG (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/epg?categoryId=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Short EPG (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/epg/short/2?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Simple Data Table (JWT Token Required)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/streaming/epg/table/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

